## **The 3-Layer Calculation Model**

### **Layer 1: Inputs (What We Capture)**

These are either pulled from Agency Snapshot or entered manually by the user.

#### **Baseline Current State (7 fields)**

| Field | Variable Name | Data Type | Source | Notes |
| ----- | ----- | ----- | ----- | ----- |
| Current Annual Revenue | `baseline_revenue` | Decimal | Agency Snapshot or manual | Most recent 12-month revenue |
| Current Team Size | `baseline_team_size` | Decimal | Agency Snapshot or manual | Full-time equivalents (FTEs) |
| Current Active Client Count | `baseline_client_count` | Integer | Agency Snapshot or manual | **NEW in V2** |
| Current Annual Retention Rate | `baseline_retention_rate` | Decimal (0-1) | Agency Snapshot or manual | **NEW in V2** (e.g., 0.85 \= 85%) |
| Current Profit Margin % | `baseline_profit_margin` | Decimal (0-1) | Agency Snapshot or manual | **NEW in V2** (EBITDA margin preferred) |
| Current Average Client Value | `baseline_acv` | Decimal | Calculated or manual | **NEW in V2** (`revenue / client_count` or entered) |
| Current AGI per FTE | `baseline_agi_per_fte` | Decimal | Agency Snapshot or calculated | **NEW in V2** (for efficiency benchmarking) |

#### **Target State (2 fields)**

| Field | Variable Name | Data Type | Source | Notes |
| ----- | ----- | ----- | ----- | ----- |
| Target Annual Revenue | `target_revenue` | Decimal | User input or Clarity Compass | The goal |
| Timeframe to Target | `target_timeframe_months` | Integer | User input | 12, 18, 24, 36, 60 months |

#### **Scenario Adjustments (5 sliders \- Pro Tier Only)**

| Slider | Variable Name | Data Type | Range | Notes |
| ----- | ----- | ----- | ----- | ----- |
| Growth Target Adjustment | `growth_adjustment_pct` | Decimal | \-50% to \+100% | **NEW in V2** \- Adjusts target revenue |
| ACV Adjustment | `acv_adjustment_pct` | Decimal | \-50% to \+100% | **NEW in V2** \- Pricing power scenario |
| Efficiency Adjustment | `efficiency_adjustment_pct` | Decimal | \-30% to \+50% | **NEW in V2** \- AGI/FTE improvement |
| Retention Improvement | `retention_adjustment_pct` | Decimal | \-20% to \+20% | **NEW in V2** \- Churn reduction |
| Margin Target Adjustment | `margin_adjustment_pct` | Decimal | \-20% to \+20% | **NEW in V2** \- Profit margin change |

**Note:** Sliders are stored as percentage deltas from baseline. When a user saves a scenario with "ACV \+30%", we store `0.30` in `acv_adjustment_pct`.

