## **Edge Cases & Guardrails**

**Input Validation:**

javascript  
*// Prevent divide-by-zero*  
if (baseline\_client\_count \< 1) baseline\_client\_count \= 1;  
if (baseline\_acv \< 100) baseline\_acv \= 100;  
if (baseline\_team\_size \< 0.5) baseline\_team\_size \= 0.5;

*// Cap adjustments at reasonable limits*  
acv\_adjustment\_pct \= Math.min(1.0, Math.max(\-0.5, acv\_adjustment\_pct));  
efficiency\_adjustment\_pct \= Math.min(0.5, Math.max(\-0.3, efficiency\_adjustment\_pct));  
retention\_adjustment\_pct \= Math.min(0.2, Math.max(\-0.2, retention\_adjustment\_pct));

*// Prevent impossible retention rates*

adjusted\_retention\_rate \= Math.min(0.99, Math.max(0.50, adjusted\_retention\_rate));

javascript  
*// Prevent divide-by-zero in ACV calculations*  
if (baseline\_acv \< 100) baseline\_acv \= 100;  
if (adjusted\_acv \< 100) adjusted\_acv \= 100;

*// Handle edge case: ACV decreases (rare but possible)*  
if (adjusted\_acv \< baseline\_acv) {  
  acv\_delta\_pct \= (adjusted\_acv \- baseline\_acv) / baseline\_acv; *// Will be negative*  
  acv\_annual\_growth\_rate \= Math.pow(adjusted\_acv / baseline\_acv, 1 / timeframe\_years) \- 1; *// Will be negative*  
  *// Note: Positioning pressure doesn't trigger for ACV decreases*  
  *// This would be a "volume play" scenario*  
}

*// Handle edge case: Zero or minimal growth*  
if (total\_revenue\_growth \=== 0 || total\_revenue\_growth \< 1000) {  
  acv\_dependency\_ratio \= 0; *// No growth means no dependency*  
}

*// Handle edge case: Pure volume play (ACV essentially constant)*  
if (Math.abs(adjusted\_acv \- baseline\_acv) \< 100) { *// Within $100*  
  acv\_delta\_pct \= 0;  
  acv\_annual\_growth\_rate \= 0;  
  acv\_dependency\_ratio \= 0;  
  *// Will trigger GREEN "Monetization Flexibility"*  
}

*// Cap dependency ratio at reasonable bounds*

acv\_dependency\_ratio \= Math.max(\-0.5, Math.min(1.5, acv\_dependency\_ratio));

